msgstr ""

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:574
msgid ""
"`stderr` (string, optional): Stderr handling strategy. Supported values:"
